### Asignar rol a usuario (aplica a todas las sedes)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/user-roles HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 2,
    "roleId": 1,
    "validFrom": "2024-01-01"
}

###

### Asignar rol a usuario en sede específica
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/user-roles HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 2,
    "roleId": 2,
    "sedeId": 1,
    "validFrom": "2024-01-01",
    "validUntil": "2026-12-31"
}

###

### Obtener asignación por ID
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/user-roles/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar todas las asignaciones
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/user-roles/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 10,
    "search": "",
    "order_by": "ur.created_at",
    "order": "DESC"
}

###

### Listar asignaciones de un usuario específico
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/user-roles/user/2 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Revocar asignación (soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:{{port}}/api/user-roles/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

